thread.title_full: DesignCrowd reviewed by ProCore Painting, LLC

author: ProCore Painting, LLC
title: ProCore Painting, LLC
text: Had DesignCrowd design my business logo for our company and they were fast, accurate, and very professional. I would recommended them to anybody who wants a great and professional looking logo in a very timely manner at very reasonable rates. I will use them again for all my future design needs.
